title: Installing GrapheneOS the Easy Way
description:
In this video I show you how to install GrapheneOS using their web USB installer
https://grapheneos.org/install/web

0:00 what kind of phone to buy
1:25 Initial setup of vanilla android
2:24 enable OEM unlocking
3:30 restarting into fastboot
4:06 unlocking bootloader
5:30 downloading GrapheneOS
6:00 flashing GrapheneOS
6:47 locking bootloader
8:30 setting up GrapheneOS
